1- Open Google and click the profile icon and &ldquo;Manage your Google Account&rdquo;. 2- On the left side click &ldquo;Personal Info&rdquo; and search &ldquo;App Passwords&rdquo;. 3- Type &ldquo;App Name&rdquo; and click &ldquo;Create&rdquo; and copy &ldquo;App Passwords&rdquo;.
5- Open Gmail and click on the settings icons top right side with the profile. 6- Go to &ldquo;Accounts and Import&rdquo; come to the &ldquo;Send mail as&rdquo; sections and click &ldquo;Add another email address&rdquo; 7- Type your &ldquo;name&rdquo; and &ldquo;email address&rdquo; and click on next.
8- SMTP Server: &ldquo;smtp.gmail.com&rdquo;
Port: 587
Username: Your Gmail address
Password: Your App Password and click &ldquo;Add Account&rdquo;

